For collision type A:

$$
\begin{aligned}
J &= m(v-u) \\
J &= 0.50 \times (2.0 - 5.0) = 0.50 \times (-3.0) = -1.5 \text{ N s}
\end{aligned}
$$

Impulse $= -1.5 \text{ N s}$ (direction indicates the force acted opposite to initial motion).

